05:47.414 --> 05:50.332
There's no respect of the innocence,

05:51.207 --> 05:54.998
no value for the innocence.

05:56.332 --> 05:59.123
They don't understand how important

05:59.539 --> 06:03.498
it is for human life

06:04.332 --> 06:07.956
to have innocence

06:08.956 --> 06:14.373
