22:08.290 --> 22:11.498
which is pure innocence,

22:11.748 --> 22:15.040
never can be contaminated

22:15.456 --> 22:18.290
by the Maya of the Mother.

22:18.498 --> 22:23.581
Maya is the process by which you test people.

22:24.123 --> 22:26.165
